Create a Dynamic Dashboard in Lightning Experience

Provide users with individualized views of data by creating a dynamic dashboard.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To create, edit, and delete dynamic dashboards: Manage Dynamic Dashboards
On the Analytics or Dashboards tab, create a dashboard or edit an existing one.
Open the properties menu by clicking .
Under View Dashboard As, select The dashboard viewer.
To let users change the dashboardâ€™s running user, select Let dashboard viewers choose whom they view the dashboard as.
Click Save.
Save your dashboard.
